title: MBMBaM 617: Platonic Neck Kisses
description:
If you’re at a loss for what to write in your Freedom Day cards, we’ve got you covered. Big ups to the self-sustaining heroes of past or whatever, but we’re focused on that giant cheese cracker, y’all. You know the one.

Suggested Talking Notes: Flimsy Man Make a Accident, Netflix's Psychic Weapon, The Clown Prince of Factual Accuracy, Legally-Mandated Sprinkle Jimmies, Orange Slog Bog, Meat Jazz

Trans Youth Equality Foundation: https://www.transyouthequality.org/
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Travis McElroy, Griffin McElroy, Justin McElroy)
